THE DEAD KING

    SPEAKS TO THE SKORAUG ABOUT THIS AFTERLIFE

    EVADES THE WORMS

    RETRIEVES A SWORD

    KILLS THE WORMS, AND EARNS AMBER
    
    SOLVES A PUZZLE INVOLVING THE SWORD

    RETRIEVES A GAUNTLET

    PASSES THROUGH A CLEARING FULL OF SPIDERS

    DISCOVERS AND SPEAKS TO A SOUL

    SPEAKS TO THE SKORAUG AND LEARNS HE MUST FIND HIS WAY TO THE MOUNTAIN VILLAGE OF WITCHES

    FINDS A SKILG AND LEARNS A RUNE
     
